# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# DEFAULT-DENY：本仓库 origin 是【公开仓库】yinheng-kk/stock-dashboard
# 默认忽略一切；只有下面显式白名单的文件才可被 git add。
# 新增公开文件必须逐个加 !/ 白名单，严禁放宽为通配。
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
/*

# ── 白名单：仓库自身 ──
!/.gitignore

# ── 白名单：公开看板页面（现有 tracked 集合）──
!/fundflow-live.html
!/fundflow-nocoxchun.html
!/fundflow_replay_core.html
!/_fundflow_replay_core.html
!/sector_fusion_dashboard.html
!/huatian_002185.html
!/zhenhua_000733.html
!/eston_002747.html

# ── 白名单：随站点提交的归档与脚本（现有 tracked 集合）──
!/_fundflow_archive/
!/_archive_fundflow_daily.py
!/_pub_fundflow_archive.py
!/_sector_fusion_daily.ps1

# ── 二级防线：即使误加白名单，密钥类文件永远忽略 ──
gh_pat.txt
gh_token_page.html
github_pat_debug.html
*pat*.txt
*.pem
*.key
*_token*.txt
*credential*
*.credentials.json
.env
.env.*
*.secret
wechat_summary.py

# ── 运行时/媒体/日志 ──
media/inbound/
*.log
*.jsonl
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.bak
*.clobbered.*
